it.uniroma3.mat.extendedset
Class ExtendedSet.Statistics

java.lang.Object
  it.uniroma3.mat.extendedset.ExtendedSet.Statistics
Enclosing interface:
ExtendedSet<T>
public static class ExtendedSet.Statistics
extends java.lang.Object

Statistical data.

In particular:

  • getIntersectionCount() counts the calls to AbstractExtendedSet.intersectionSet(Collection)
  • getUnionCount() counts the calls to AbstractExtendedSet.unionSet(Collection)
  • getSymmetricDifferenceCount() counts the calls to AbstractExtendedSet.symmetricDifferenceSet(Collection)
  • getDifferenceCount() counts the calls to AbstractExtendedSet.differenceSet(Collection)
  • getSizeCheckCount() counts the calls to AbstractExtendedSet.intersectionSize(Collection), AbstractExtendedSet.unionSize(Collection), AbstractExtendedSet.symmetricDifferenceSize(Collection), AbstractExtendedSet.differenceSize(Collection)
  • getEqualsCount() counts the calls to AbstractSet.equals(Object)
NOTE: no counting is done for AbstractExtendedSet.complementSet() and AbstractExtendedSet.complementSize() since they are very fast.
